                            <p>GO STEM is a collaborative partnership led by an Advisory Board with representatives from seven counties in eastern Oregon. Our work centers around three key priority areas:</p>
                            <ol>
                                <li> STEM Awareness, Pipelines & Pathways – Grow the workforce!

                                <li> STEM Systems for Education – Improve educational opportunities!

